# Cowork Forge - AI Context Snapshot
# Generated: 2026-03-28
# Purpose: Minimal context for AI agents to understand project structure

## PROJECT OVERVIEW

name: cowork-forge
type: rust-workspace
edition: "2024"
version: "2.5.0"
description: AI-native iterative software development platform with multi-agent orchestration

## CRATES STRUCTURE

### cowork-core
path: crates/cowork-core/
role: domain-logic-core
description: Core library with domain entities, pipeline orchestration, tools, and persistence
entry_points:
  - src/lib.rs
key_modules:
  - pipeline: 7-stage workflow orchestration
  - domain: Project, Iteration, Memory aggregates (DDD)
  - tools: 30+ ADK tools for file/memory/HITL operations
  - persistence: JSON-based storage layer
  - interaction: InteractiveBackend trait for CLI/GUI abstraction
  - agents: Agent builders using adk-rust framework
  - instructions: ~2000 lines of prompt engineering
  - config_definition: V3 data-driven configuration system
  - skills: agentskills.io standard integration
  - acp: External coding agent protocol client

### cowork-cli
path: crates/cowork-cli/
role: cli-adapter
description: Command-line interface with clap
entry: src/main.rs
commands: [init, iter, list, show, continue, status, delete, import, knowledge, config]

### cowork-gui
path: crates/cowork-gui/
role: gui-adapter
description: Tauri-based desktop application with React frontend
backend_entry: src-tauri/src/main.rs
frontend_entry: src/main.tsx
features: [project-dashboard, iteration-management, artifact-viewer, chat-interface, app-preview]

## CORE CONCEPTS

### 7-Stage Pipeline
stages:
  - id: idea
    description: Capture and structure requirements
    artifact: idea.md
    hitl: false
  - id: prd
    description: Generate Product Requirements Document
    artifact: prd.md
    hitl: true
    pattern: actor-critic
  - id: design
    description: Create technical architecture
    artifact: design.md
    hitl: true
    pattern: actor-critic
  - id: plan
    description: Break down implementation tasks
    artifact: plan.md
    hitl: true
    pattern: actor-critic
  - id: coding
    description: Implement code with tests
    artifact: workspace/
    hitl: true
    pattern: actor-critic
  - id: check
    description: Verify quality and completeness
    artifact: check_report.md
    hitl: false
  - id: delivery
    description: Generate final delivery report
    artifact: delivery_report.md
    hitl: false

### Iteration Types
types:
  - name: genesis
    description: First iteration, fresh start
    inheritance: none
  - name: evolution
    description: Build upon previous iteration
    inheritance_modes: [full, partial, none]

### Inheritance Modes
modes:
  - name: none
    description: Fresh start, no inheritance
    start_stage: idea
  - name: partial
    description: Copy artifacts only, regenerate code
    start_stage: idea (configurable)
  - name: full
    description: Copy all code and artifacts
    start_stage: configurable

### Actor-Critic Pattern
description: Each critical stage uses Actor-Critic loop
flow:
  - actor: Generates artifacts based on instructions
  - critic: Validates quality, suggests improvements
  - hitl: Human confirms or provides feedback
  - revision: Actor regenerates with feedback if needed

## KEY DATA STRUCTURES

### Project (Aggregate Root)
location: crates/cowork-core/src/domain/project.rs
fields:
  - id: String
  - name: String
  - metadata: ProjectMetadata (tech_stack, project_type, language)
  - current_iteration_id: Option<String>
  - iterations: Vec<IterationSummary>

### Iteration
location: crates/cowork-core/src/domain/iteration.rs
fields:
  - id: String
  - number: u32
  - title: String
  - description: String
  - base_iteration_id: Option<String>
  - inheritance: InheritanceMode
  - status: IterationStatus (Draft/Running/Paused/Completed/Failed)
  - current_stage: Option<String>
  - completed_stages: Vec<String>
  - artifacts: Artifacts

### Artifacts
location: crates/cowork-core/src/domain/iteration.rs
fields:
  - idea: Option<String> (path to idea.md)
  - prd: Option<String> (path to prd.md)
  - design: Option<String> (path to design.md)
  - plan: Option<String> (path to plan.md)
  - coding: Option<String> (workspace path)
  - delivery: Option<String> (path to delivery_report.md)

### ProjectMemory
location: crates/cowork-core/src/domain/memory.rs
fields:
  - decisions: Vec<Decision>
  - patterns: Vec<Pattern>
  - issues: Vec<Issue>
  - learnings: Vec<Learning>

### IterationKnowledge
location: crates/cowork-core/src/domain/memory.rs
fields:
  - iteration_id: String
  - decisions: Vec<Decision>
  - patterns: Vec<Pattern>
  - issues: Vec<Issue>
  - learnings: Vec<Learning>
  - tech_stack: Vec<String>

## CRITICAL PATHS

### Iteration Execution Entry
file: crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/executor/mod.rs
function: IterationExecutor::execute()
flow:
  1. Load iteration from IterationStore
  2. Prepare workspace (inherit if evolution)
  3. Determine start stage from inheritance mode
  4. Execute stages sequentially
  5. Handle HITL gates at critical stages
  6. Complete iteration and generate knowledge

### Stage Execution
file: crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/stage_executor.rs
trait: Stage
methods:
  - name(): &str
  - description(): &str
  - needs_confirmation(): bool
  - execute(ctx, interaction): StageResult
  - execute_with_feedback(ctx, interaction, feedback): StageResult

### HITL Flow
file: crates/cowork-core/src/interaction/mod.rs
trait: InteractiveBackend
methods:
  - show_message(level, content)
  - send_streaming(content, agent_name, is_thinking)
  - send_tool_call(tool_name, arguments, agent_name)
  - request_input(prompt, options, initial_content): InputResponse
  - show_progress(task_id, progress)

### Tool Registry
file: crates/cowork-core/src/tools/mod.rs
categories:
  - file_tools: ReadFileTool, WriteFileTool, ListFilesTool
  - data_tools: CreateRequirementTool, AddFeatureTool, GetRequirementsTool, CreateTaskTool
  - hitl_tools: ReviewWithFeedbackContentTool, ProvideFeedbackTool
  - memory_tools: QueryMemoryTool, SaveInsightTool, SaveIssueTool
  - validation_tools: CheckFeatureCoverageTool, CheckTaskDependenciesTool
  - control_tools: GotoStageTool
  - artifact_tools: SaveIdeaTool, SavePrdDocTool, SaveDesignDocTool

