  - StageDefinition: Stage behavior configuration
  - FlowDefinition: Workflow pipeline configuration
  - SkillDefinition: agentskills.io integration
  - IntegrationDefinition: External system hooks

## STORAGE STRUCTURE

### .cowork-v2/ Directory
location: <project-root>/.cowork-v2/
structure:
  - project.json: Project metadata
  - memory.json: ProjectMemory (cross-iteration knowledge)
  - iterations/
    - iter-<number>-<timestamp>/
      - iteration.json: Iteration metadata
      - memory.json: IterationKnowledge
      - artifacts/
        - idea.md
        - prd.md
        - design.md
        - plan.md
        - delivery_report.md
      - workspace/: Generated code files

## EXTERNAL INTEGRATIONS

### ACP (Agent Communication Protocol)
location: crates/cowork-core/src/acp/
purpose: External coding agent integration
supported_agents: [opencode, iflow, codex, gemini, claude]
transport: [stdio, websocket]

### Skills (agentskills.io)
location: crates/cowork-core/src/skills/
purpose: Domain-specific capability injection
discovery: .skills/ directory
categories: [web_frontend, web_backend, mobile, devops, testing, security]

## IMPORTANT CONSTRAINTS

### Rate Limiting
- LLM API: 30 requests/minute, concurrency=1
- Implementation: Semaphore + 2s delay decorator

### Security
- Path validation for all file operations
- Workspace containment (no access outside project)
- Command sanitization for shell execution
- Dangerous commands blocked (rm -rf, sudo, etc.)

### HITL Gates
- Critical stages (idea, prd, design, plan, coding) require human confirmation
- Max revision loops: 5 per stage
- Max stage retries: 3

## DEPENDENCIES

### Core Framework
- adk-rust: Agent framework (v0.4.0)
- tokio: Async runtime
- serde/serde_json: Serialization

### UI
- clap: CLI argument parsing
- tauri: Desktop application framework
- react: GUI frontend
- ant-design: UI components

### LLM
- OpenAI-compatible APIs
- Streaming response support
